01/2014:
In this very directory we will create the CFS++ Data Analysis Tool (cfsdat) 
We plan to create a unified interface for CFS++ users for:
- File Conversion
- FFT
- Aeroacoustic source term computation
- Evaluation of results at given points or along lines
- General data analysis (diff|sum|etc.) as provided by current cfstool
- Interpolation of Data to other grids
- Generation of analytical fields on boundaries or inside the domain
  based on the given HDF5 files

Some parts of the programm should also be capable to include MPI-functionality
This is a crucial thing and we have to see how this can be established.
Perhaps we can seperate some parts of the programm as MPI...

First Steps:
1. Establish a hirarchical command line interface using boost
2. Create the first module for analytic fields
